<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/7/27/21340993/intel-hardware-chief-venkata-murthy-renduchintala-leaving">英特尔调整公司架构，硬件主管将离职</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354454" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Murthy_Renduchintala_print_02.0.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Murthy_Renduchintala_print_02.0.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Murthy_Renduchintala_print_02.0-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Murthy_Renduchintala_print_02.0-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Murthy_Renduchintala_print_02.0-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，英特尔宣布其硬件主管 Dr. Venkata（Murthy）Renduchintala 将于 8 月 3 日离职。英特尔于 2016 年从高通挖来 Renduchintala，他主要负责芯片和其它硬件业务管理。今天，这统一团队也被拆分为五个不同的团队，五个团队的负责人将直接向 CEO 汇报。</p>
<p>最近，英特尔宣布其下一代 7 纳米芯片需推迟到 2022 年发布，而其 10 纳米处理器的研发也已经推迟了数年。</p>
<h4>微信车载版将登陆 BMW</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354456" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/w700h350z1l10t100f1.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="350" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/w700h350z1l10t100f1.jpg 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/w700h350z1l10t100f1-360x180.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
<p>宝马与腾讯宣布开展数字化合作，双方将共同推进车载轻应用生态「腾讯小场景」和「微信车载版」在 BMW 车上的应用。</p>
<p>「腾讯小场景」是专为出行场景打造的车载轻应用生态，基于云端更新，无需下载安装，支持语音交互。支持全语音交互「微信车载版」则让用户在安全驾驶的同时，保持社交沟通不掉线。</p>
<h4><a href="https://techcrunch.com/2020/07/27/garmin-confirms-ransomware-attack-outage/">佳明确认遭黑客攻击，用户数据曾无法同步</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354457" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/garmin.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/garmin.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/garmin-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/garmin-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/garmin-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>TechCrunch 消息，佳明确认公司于 7 月 23 日遭到黑客攻击，导致其网页、客服、用户应用和企业沟通均受到影响，用户活动的数据也无法同步。佳明表示，没有迹象显示用户数据遭到泄露，所有服务预计将于本周恢复正常。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/4733748.html">娃哈哈首个奶茶直营店落地广州</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354458" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2c16c0beecb346378f29276642bb9efa.jpeg" alt="" width="1080" height="705" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2c16c0beecb346378f29276642bb9efa.jpeg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2c16c0beecb346378f29276642bb9efa-360x235.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2c16c0beecb346378f29276642bb9efa-768x501.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2c16c0beecb346378f29276642bb9efa-1024x668.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>界面消息，娃哈哈近日在广州开出首家直营奶茶店，销售以娃哈哈 AD 钙奶和乳酸钙奶为原料的茶饮，定价在 12-22 元间。</p>
<p>值得指出的是，虽然说是直营店，娃哈哈总部并不负责门店运营，而是通过品牌授权给合作伙伴经营。此前，娃哈哈奶茶店已经以加盟店的形式在国内开出三百多个门店。</p>
